{"tid":30594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CY棄選葉劉直言好可惜：睇電視好感動","createTime":"2016-12-09T08:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T09:52:06.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"231f5b0ba0c4c16d3cad821cd51fed7d0db06bc0","tid":30594,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161209/large/1481272453_ce73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161209%2Flarge%2F1481272453_ce73.jpg&h=ea91f75f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首梁振英下午突然見記者，稱為照顧家庭，宣佈不爭取連任；熱門候選人之一立法會議員葉劉淑儀回應指，對梁振英不爭連任感可惜。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀指與梁遊振英在行會共事4年，稱贊他工作認真，直言看梁在電視上發表聲明時「好感動亦都好同情」，因知道他為減輕家庭壓力而放棄競選。葉又指梁振英過去4年不辭勞苦為香港人做事，尤其在房屋土地方面值得欣賞。<br />\n<br />\n對於是否增加了她參選的意願，她說是言之過早，「最重要有個公平公開有競爭嘅選舉，政治一日都嫌長」。"},{"pid":"ec82f128be71b7b07eeb96ec1d65e1a06a36d602","tid":30594,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:41:52.000Z","msg":"嘴角微翹<br />\n明顯忍緊笑"},{"pid":"158a8a6ed8f8b910d5d915a7824f076e998a293f","tid":30594,"uid":59480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:44:16.000Z","msg":"今晚一定開心到訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3296a04ce72d647b051d586aaddf070bde6fe696","tid":30594,"uid":3123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:43:12.000Z","msg":"少鳩左個對手緊係感動啦"},{"pid":"8ecffb68a86da800ad320841c91102950508ce5d","tid":30594,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:44:20.000Z","msg":"何方妖孽"},{"pid":"f8ff3268b77ee057a98e7774b87cb866d345833c","tid":30594,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:45:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de7e9eea2c9a8e9c00d410c5903fcc663ed8947e","tid":30594,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:45:23.000Z","msg":"